List all containers
=docker ps -a=

Create new container
=docker run --name name -d -t ubuntu=

=docker run --name name -d -t ubuntu:16.04=

|------+-------------|
| Flag | Description |
|------+-------------|
| =-d= | Daemonize   |
| =-t= | Enable TTY  |
|------+-------------|

Run container
=docker exec -t name /bin/bash=

